@TaskFlow.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5005

### Info (anonymous)
GET {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Register
POST {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "userName": "demo.user",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass",
  "confirmPassword": "Str0ng!Pass",
  "organizationName": "Acme Workspace"
}

###

### Login
POST {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass"
}

###

### Me (set @token from login/register response)
@token = paste_jwt_here

GET {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Workspace (returns a new JWT)
POST {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/workspaces
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Workspace"
}

### Note:
### This endpoint returns a fresh JWT (with new org_id). Copy it and update @token below.
@token = paste_new_jwt_here

### Join Workspace (switch org using join code)
POST {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/workspaces/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "PASTE_JOIN_CODE"
}

### After join, copy returned JWT and call /api/auth/me again.
@token = paste_new_jwt_here_after_join

GET {{TaskFlow.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
